Please use the following format on the C program comments


1. For functions
                    /**
                    * Method description.
                    * @param param1 param1 description 
                    * @param param2 param2 description
                    * @return return description
                    * @since date since function is created
                    * @author who have made this function.
                    */


2. For variables
                    /** variables description **/


3. For Structures
                    /**
                    * Structure description.
                    * @since date since structure is created
                    * @author who have made this structure.
                    */